frames.caption: A majestic angelic figure stands amidst swirling clouds, wielding a flaming sword. Clad in ornate silver armor, the figure's large wings are spread wide, and lightning crackles in the stormy sky behind.
frames.description: The scene depicts a powerful, mythical setting featuring an angelic warrior. The atmosphere is dramatic and intense, with elements of fantasy and divine power.

frames.caption: A young knight stands resolute amidst a stormy sky, gripping a glowing sword. His armor gleams as lightning crackles around him, highlighting his determined expression.
frames.description: The scene depicts a fantasy setting where a knight is poised for battle. The dramatic sky filled with dark clouds and lightning adds to the epic atmosphere.
